@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tuogiu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((0.72 + wp.abs(v1 + 0.31)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v2 + 0.90) * (v2 + 0.48 / v2 + 0.57)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
